hvtE/19" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;em style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;订阅华盛顿版时事通讯，&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;em style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;了解来自美国首都的新闻，并在美国东部时间工作日下午 1 点和 5 点观看彭博电视台的《权力平衡》节目。&lt;/em&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 style="font-size: 24px; line-height: 30px; font-weight: 700; padding-top: 12px; border-top: 1px solid; margin-top: 40px;"&gt;每日图表&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;figure style="margin: 20px 0;"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="580"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ipeBXm4.eaME/v3/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKsrX.ke8XuWirGYh1PKgEw44kE/-1x-1.png" alt="" width="580"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="替代" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ipeBXm4.eaME/v3/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKsrX.ke8XuWirGYh1PKgEw44kE/-1x-1.png" style="width: 100%; display: block; margin-bottom: 4px;" /&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;德意志银行的Jacky Tang表示，随着战争给石油和天然气市场带来极大的波动，全球能源安全竞赛正在&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/ALq-P1Vy04tkf-eo2INN1tam2GQgbdpV99KCM3cs32yDglKvdjjLktkZYRd3-l0rGvNutkHMebZGkYi7OBs4jfHafTmGfHtrlqLo_A2estTbFRtzky9PeKMEYE1PrkvVzxMWkOXS6OGvWCk2MNFe1jj5XhEZBbqomd16iZNIccbXgXGY54wcF7QzcSlMTPa-DrUiKAxiBX-W2JcXljMcohim0qeffAFcqrvcf2cr629IVbwJ3o8LsP4xVflIkXECOzfjYpguS6wBMMjBO4M5j54AngfguOiswLdUB1yUddznKoHJudIEXiA8MxOCFtNzrvb1daDdp7s8gLhzEvf7N4XCAryoQxTgOF7PWyeua7zJQlOhMD7kiVvXpkCVwn6_1hrpQjgn0Lp-9NwhpmZ8DzAHI4slGebrVauR3QWEKRywp-PPvgygEOz1aOenlHC6SIBCFJan7QR5uiqji3S23HO9oqjzyeL6Il_x0bYzX9IDqzjIeQDR49vs35dRYzkiXJfLv2-osXLWH73sbA/4f2mESjidgbf8cO_xXu8Lqlt4mqyQu7m/19" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="德意志银行称中国是战争时代的能源“赢家”"&gt;使中国变得更加强大&lt;/a&gt;。这一预测形成了一幅复杂的图景。尽管智库布鲁盖尔表示，北京对从伊朗进口石油的依赖将对其能源战略构成“严峻考验”，但唐表示，中国作为全球最大的清洁技术生产商的地位使其处于独特的地位，可以帮助目前迫切需要摆脱对中东进口的各国政府。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 style="font-size: 24px; line-height: 30px; font-weight: 700; padding-top: 12px; border-top: 1px solid; margin-top: 40px;"&gt;最后&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;朝鲜本周进行了一系列新武器&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/BSqj4YMd-HG5jrbRITeycmVkoXox8-ByJ1ugaHSes8mf_7A2C-SJiYOk3507rAbqUpUndVlL7PiIA607NDLBP8qTko7aXWl6JXc-N4oq-sBYjXV-hFIVANB47H6RthQ5WHZmrWBvfWOYFY7sPEm3L4EjNvOjWANKh9t8ovaaX15PgE39Lbgzcrm565SkHnMH3o0MpbOLengjaqZVNiGNZ8x7aRBtwTuBcJmeHC1CzJAtFpGcRYOdlPTzxHc5bbWYUhiZwMMKwjA-T4j2ueJCs-7EDUPYbbC3h6z2PF9rGdW4i8it7w3nR9pUiHgUcidPOQYUewRPxBNC0t8LelBXaFzPU8Qc2aqVv57xJez_M4QpEaH5WSi3gU5GPQ3y8DPNcdgud7OQzqRwmjsc0EhL73hx8LbDfNK32dxMI_iC6PmXrG7V_pC1isXFKHqR-VSmZfrqDNC1ibIz6t4oebKCQBhcUTsPMfCSb4e_GrR8NkCe1uH4VarayryJ0_qTo-YPsqsusOnG6OAVusYPK-CuEsdDuoi10Q/lXVOMIJjPBDhAcp72LQnuGcI_R836qx6/19" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="世界聚焦伊朗，朝鲜测试最新武器"&gt;测试&lt;/a&gt;，包括电磁武器系统和防空导弹，同时加大了常规武器升级力度。这些测试是在地缘政治不确定性加剧之际进行的，导致美国军事资产撤离亚洲，而平壤则继续深化与莫斯科的关系，并在与北京的现有关系的基础上再接再厉。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;figure style="margin: 20px 0;"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="580"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iwHHlMjum2JQ/v0/-1x-1.jpg" alt="This picture taken on March 3, 2026 and released by North Korea&amp;amp;#39;s official Korean Central News Agency (KCNA) on March 5, 2026 shows North Korean leader Kim Jong Un (C) inspecting a shooting competition to mark the Korean People&amp;amp;#39;s Army&amp;amp;#39;s &amp;amp;quot;Snipers&amp;amp;#39; Day&amp;amp;quot; at a training base in Pyongyang. (Photo by KCNA VIA KNS &amp;amp;#x2F; AFP via Getty Images) &amp;amp;#x2F; South Korea OUT &amp;amp;#x2F; ---EDITORS NOTE--- RESTRICTED TO EDITORIAL USE - MANDATORY CREDIT &amp;amp;quot;AFP PHOTO&amp;amp;#x2F;KCNA VIA KNS&amp;amp;quot; - NO MARKETING NO ADVERTISING CAMPAIGNS - DISTRIBUTED AS A SERVICE TO CLIENTS THIS PICTURE WAS MADE AVAILABLE BY A THIRD